            "text": "Statistics  ️",
            "note": "deals with the collection, analysis, interpretation, presentation and organisation of data  it deals with all aspects of data including the planning of data collection in terms of the design of surveys and experiments  in applying statistics to a problem, it is common practice to start with a population or process to be studied  populations can be diverse topics such as ‘all persons living in a country’ or ‘every atom composing a crystal’",
