              {
                "text": "Set theory  ️",
                "note": "study of sets where sets are collections of objects  we refer to these objects as “elements” “members” of the set  to write a set, one wraps the numbers in {curly brackets} and separates them with commas:   e.g. {1,2,3} holds 1, 2 and 3  was invented in 1874",
